summary: Changes those ugly undies to sexy thongs, me gusta
descriptionHtml:
Hi all,

I like playing with female chars, but hate the ugly underwear, so therefor i thought lets put some work behind that thought and this is the result!

Hope you enjoy it.

How to install:
- Put the texture folder in your data folder (c\\program files\\skyrim\\data)
- Put the meshes folder in your data folder
